casebody.head_matter:
Daniel RODRIGUEZ, Petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES;
Julio Rivera-Lopez, Petitioner,
v.
United States;
Kristian Torres, Petitioner,
v.
United States.
No. 18-9266
Supreme Court of the United States.
October 7, 2019
On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit. Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit for further consideration in light of United States v. Davis , 588 U.S. ----, 139 S.Ct. 2319, 204 L.Ed.2d 757 (2019).
